quran[13{c,v,t}:
21,45,"inn se keh do ke"" mein to wahi ki bana par tumhe mutnabba kar raha hon"" magar behray pukaar ko nahi suna karte jabkay unhen khabardaar kya jaye"
21,46,"aur agar tairay rab ka azaab zara sa inhen chhoo jaye to abhi cheekh utheen ke haae hamari kam bakhti, be shak hum khata waar thay"
21,47,"qayamat ke roz hum theek theek tolnay walay traazo rakh den ge, phir kisi shakhs par zarra barabar zulm nah ho ga jis ka rai ke danay ke barabar bhi kuch kya dhara ho ga woh hum samnay le ayen ge aur hisaab laganay ke liye hum kaafi hain"
21,48,"pehlay hum moose aur haroon ko Farqan aur roshni aur"" zikar"" ataa kar chuke hain unn mut-taqi logon ki BHALAI ke liye"
21,49,jo be dekhe apne rab se dareen aur jin ko ( hisaab ki ) uss gharri ka khatka laga howa hai
21,50,"aur ab yeh babarkat"" zikar"" hum ne ( tumahray liye ) nazil kya hai phir kya tum iss ko qubool karne se inkari ho ?"
21,51,uss se bhi pehlay hum ne ibrahim ko uss ki hosh mandi bakhsh thi aur hum uss ko khoob jantay thay
21,52,"yaad karo woh mauqa jabkay uss ne apne baap aur apni qoum se kaha tha ke"" yeh moorten kaisi hain jin ke tum log garweedah ho rahay ho? """
21,53,"unhon ne jawab diya"" hum ne apne baap dada ko un ki ibadat karte paaya hai """
21,54,"is ne kaha"" tum bhi gumraah ho aur tumahray baap dada bhi Sarih gumraahi mein parre hue thay? """
21,55,"unhon ne kaha"" kya to hamaray samnay apne asli khayalat paish kar raha hai ya mazaq karta hai? """
21,56,"uss ne jawab diya"" nahi, balkay fi al waqea tumhara rab wohi hai jo zameen aur asmano ka rab aur unn ka peda karne wala hai iss par mein tumahray samnay gawahi deta hon"
21,57,"aur khuda ki qasam mein tumhari ghair mojoodgi mein zaroor tumahray buton ki khabar lon ga """
